channel.title: Pissing me off...At it for 2 hours Lol
channel.description: Wow. This is probably the stupidest question I have ever asked, and doubt it will get answered. I was making 1v1 work like RuneScape, and started fixing a bug. Now its giving me these stupid errors for some reason. Like the int that defines it is right above it, and it can't find the symbol. And now it gives me an error saying it can't return a method which type is void is false or something. My question, Kind of, Is...Did I delete something? Or do something wrong... I've been fucking with this for 2 hours.
